>>57ebb4d9-8a96-4605-a9c1-68528a5947f4
I know you're just comparing 4pol and 8pol, but 8chan as a site was undeniably superior. 8chan had user created boards and allowed tor & vpn posting. 8chan had dedicated christian boards. When catholics overran the main board and censored dissent, we could just go make another board that didn't censor.

8chan boards were exactly as censorious as the userbase would tolerate, and global moderation basically only deleted cp.
